This is a "Lock" demo for the feature FSM (Finite State Machine) of Akka.

See: http://cntt.tv/nodes/show/559

You should have Git and SBT. To run:

1. Install Akka 1.0-SNAPSHOT

cd /tmp
git clone http://github.com/jboner/akka.git
cd akka
sbt update
sbt publish-local

2. Run the demo in SBT console

cd /tmp
git clone http://github.com/ngocdaothanh/lock-fsm-akka.git
cd lock-fsm-akka
sbt update
sbt console

3. From the console, input

import akka.actor.Actor
import demo.{Lock, Button}
val l = Actor.actorOf(new Lock("2552"))
l.start
l ! Button('2')
l ! Button('5')
l ! Button('5')
l ! Button('2')
l.stop
exit
